<div class="abc group">
		<h3 class="full">New in Airfoil 4</h3>
		
		<div class="main-a">
			<ol class="lst">
				<li>
					<img src="images/featureicons/reverseconnect.png" style="width: 32px; height: 32px"  alt="Reverse Connect Icon" />
					<strong>Reverse Connect</strong>
					Airfoil Speakers can now initiate connections back to Airfoil, to start receiving audio remotely.
				</li>				
				<li class="last">
				<img src="/global/images/icons/32/instanthijack32.png"  style="width: 32px; height: 32px" alt="icon" />
